BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 19 Apr (MENA)--Foreign Minister 'Amr Musa has 
announced that arangements are being made to convene an 
emergency meeting soon of the Islamic Conference Organization to 
discuss the developments in the city of Gorazde in Bosnia. 
  'Amr Musa affirmed at a news conference today that what is 
happening in Gorazde is just another piece of evidence of the 
failure of international politics to deal with this issue. 

